{"tid":1697936,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"原定區選日開賽　UNICEF慈善跑安全為由取消","createTime":"2019-11-07T07:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T07:24:16.000Z","uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e4bb5a37705826b6d68a07a527bd4b6adaf7804c","tid":1697936,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20191107/s00006/af52c98cfb41e04908bdd6e89dd222b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20191107%2Fs00006%2Faf52c98cfb41e04908bdd6e89dd222b6.jpg&h=3ebc5bad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聯合國兒童基金香港委員會（UNICEF HK）今日宣布，因應連串持續及不確定因累，取消本月24日上演的「為兒童跑」賽事，以保障參加者及義工等安全。賽會將向跑手及捐助者派發感謝禮包，亦可申請退回捐款。<br />\n<br />\nUNICEF為兒童跑原定本月24日，在香港迪士尼樂園度假區及欣澳舉行，比賽日同時為區議會選舉日。賽會今日宣布，經審慎思量後，鑑於連串持續且不確定的因素，可能影響賽事，為保障跑手、義工、嘉賓等安全，決定取消賽事。「為兒童跑」原本設3公里至半馬拉松組別，當中有親子組及兒童組。<br />\n<br />\n賽會將向跑手及捐助者派發禮包，亦可經電郵發出的表格申請退回捐款，詳情可登上 <a href=\"http://unicef.org.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funicef.org.hk&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNco9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=2cd06522\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">unicef.org.hk</a> 查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/體育/article/20191107/s00006/1573111207519/【長跑】原定區選日開賽-unicef慈善跑安全為由取消\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2Farticle%2F20191107%2Fs00006%2F1573111207519%2F%E3%80%90%E9%95%B7%E8%B7%91%E3%80%91%E5%8E%9F%E5%AE%9A%E5%8D%80%E9%81%B8%E6%97%A5%E9%96%8B%E8%B3%BD-unicef%E6%85%88%E5%96%84%E8%B7%91%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%82%BA%E7%94%B1%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNco9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=511db29f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2Farticle%2F20191107%2Fs00006%2F1573111207519%2F%E3%80%90%E9%95%B7%E8%B7%91%E3%80%91%E5%8E%9F%E5%AE%9A%E5%8D%80%E9%81%B8%E6%97%A5%E9%96%8B%E8%B3%BD-unicef%E6%85%88%E5%96%84%E8%B7%91%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%82%BA%E7%94%B1%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88&h=30d446fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/體育/article/20191107/s00006/1573111207519/【長跑】原定區選日開賽-unicef慈善跑安全為由取消</a>"},{"pid":"541fd9b7939fcd22e273e6b68c2bf245f60e29d7","tid":1697936,"uid":313198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T07:24:16.000Z","msg":"想放棄想輸，入嚟聽完首歌再決定<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697147</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}